{"tid":1904930,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實香港人都杯葛咗功能組別23年，爭取到啲咩？","createTime":"2020-03-01T01:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T02:58:19.000Z","uid":63045,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8f3312077630bc10feda7dc9b4022e50ad1ae895","tid":1904930,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T01:37:17.000Z","msg":"駱惠寧教埋你點奪權都唔識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n終於知點解近排咁多五毛，因為功能組別已登記選民<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4月2號截止</span>更改，所以要配合中聯辦出盡奶力扮激進叫人杯葛<br />\n<br />\n咪做咗23年白票撚囉，香港過去邊有人理功能組別，結果有冇得取消功能組別啊？？五毛出黎講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 杯葛功能組別然後取消功能組別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜野邏輯？叫美國幫你取消功能組別仲好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲人仲揾加入警隊改變警隊黎做類比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加入警隊做散仔幾十隻眼望住你，有晒你record，緊係無可能啦。立會點同啊，上星期要否決你狗隊加人工就否決你，吹咩？<br />\n<br />\n快啲一齊玩爛個制度，送份新上任禮物比駱生賀一賀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再送班柒頭小數派番屋企做失業大軍<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實立法全面直選有配票中共唔係應該仲易玩？？<br />\nbtw2 有冇it人整個懶人網幫人睇下自己合資格申請邊個功能組別<br />\nbtw3 預言五毛會四月頭暫時消失，七八月再蒲頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b9ed6d44b149ecaa8020c1238a838aba1a1f20","tid":1904930,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T01:38:11.000Z","msg":"係屋企無野做就上網睇下個遊戲點玩"},{"p